==English==

===Etymology===
Malay "forest people".

===Noun===
'''orangutan''' 
# An [[arboreal]] [[anthropoid]] [[ape]] genus ''[[Pongo]]'' consisting of two species, ''Pongo pygmaeus'' of [[Borneo]] and ''P. abelii'' of [[Sumatra]], having a [[shaggy]] [[reddish]]-[[brown]] [[coat]], very long [[arm]]s, and no [[tail]].

